-- Obama says moderating job losses "encouraging"
-- 
-- Fri May 8, 2009 11:48am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/05/08/us-usa-economy-payrolls-obama-sb-idUSTRE5473Z820090508

 

 WASHINGTON  (Reuters) - President Barack Obama said on Friday the latest figures showing moderating job losses were encouraging but also sobering and said there were signs of progress. 

